* `backend/app/api/routes.py`
  * `/signals/next`  GET – returns current trade suggestions.
  * `/trades/approve/{signal_id}`  POST – approve trade (semi-auto).
  * `/settings/` CRUD endpoints.

### 2.  Market Data adapters
* Under `backend/app/data/`, write:
