### 3.  Strategy Engine
* `backend/app/strategy/base.py` – abstract `Strategy` class with `on_bar`, `on_quote`, etc.
* `backend/app/strategy/scalping.py` – example momentum/mean-reversion scalping strategy.
* `backend/app/strategy/swing.py` – EMA crossover + ML probability.
* `backend/app/strategy/options.py` – simplistic vertical spread seller (uses option chain endpoint).
* Add `AIHelper` util that:
  * Sends latest headline text to LLM, returns sentiment score.
  * Caches results to Redis.

### 4.  Risk Management
* `backend/app/risk/manager.py`
  * Position sizing via fixed-fraction or Kelly fraction.
  * Check max risk per trade, per day, portfolio VAR.
  * Attach stop-loss / take-profit to trade.
  * Expose `risk_manager.validate(signal) -> ApprovedSignal | RejectedSignal`.

### 5.  Execution Engine
* `backend/app/execution/router.py`
  * Converts ApprovedSignal to Alpaca order (market/limit).
  * Handles partial fills, smart-routes if dark-pool (simulated).
  * Emits `OrderEvent` to event bus and persists to DB.

### 6.  Model Server micro-service
* Separate FastAPI `backend/model_server/main.py`
  * `/predict/price` – returns probability of up-move given JSON features.
  * Loads lightweight XGBoost model from `models/xgb_price.bin`.
  * `/llm/sentiment` – proxy to OpenAI completions (or local model).
  * Use `asyncio`, rely on ENV `OPENAI_API_KEY`.

### 7.  Celery Tasks
